<br />
After getting the easier skills up to 300, I tried to get smithing up and spent about 6-7 hours of farming for 40 combines. That got me total of 2 points. This is current system, not the new proposed system. That means I would have to spend over 150 hours of farming for me to get from 250 to 300. That's on top of all the raids I need to attend and XP groups I need to AAs to get better at tradeskills. And it will only get worse after these changes go in. <br />
<br />
